{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2016/07/sublime-text-plugin-nodejs.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"38d0e043-b4da-5617-8df5-f7ef4b5f5250","html":"<p>Trước mình có viết 1 bài về giới thiệu Sublime Text, các <a href=\"https://blog.duyet.net/2014/03/sublime-text-3-editor-manh-me-cho-lap.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">plugin hay cho lập trình viên PHP</a>. Hôm nay mình sẽ giới thiệu 1 số plugin cần có để lập trình Node.js trên Sublime.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.duyet.net/2016/07/sublime-text-plugin-nodejs.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Vk9xy2-YHhQ/V476BZ29wmI/AAAAAAAAaC8/dzgxlK1P5nQ-GNPbynkCDUxxHmwYl4rxACK4B/s1600/package-control-duyetdev.gif\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"html-css-js-prettify\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#html-css-js-prettify\" aria-label=\"html css js prettify permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/HTML-CSS-JS%20Prettify\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">HTML-CSS-JS Prettify</a></h2>\n<p>Plugin này cho phép bạn định dạng pretty code cho Javascript, HTML, CSS và cả JSON. Bạn có thể tùy chỉnh lại định dạng cho phù hợp với phong cách cá nhân hoặc của cả team, hỗ trợ local config bằng file <code class=\"language-text\">.jsbeautifyrc</code>.</p>\n<p>Cài đặt:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Nhấn <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+Shift+P</code> hoặc <code class=\"language-text\">Cmd+Shift+P</code></li>\n<li>Gõ <code class=\"language-text\">install</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Package Control: Install Package</code></li>\n<li>Gõ <code class=\"language-text\">prettify</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">HTML-CSS-JS Prettify</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"nodejs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nodejs\" aria-label=\"nodejs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Nodejs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Nodejs</a></h2>\n<p>Plugin cung cấp chức năng tự động completion code, gợi ý hàm cho các module, một số công cụ để lập trình Node (run code, debug, Uglify, NPM trực tiếp trong Sublime, Build, …).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-tARsdYCr6hw/V47mwpshkBI/AAAAAAAAaB8/RvpFLnPwwBcjTJgGMBDDYesZgqlKBDeCgCK4B/s1600/node-plugin-subl.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-tARsdYCr6hw/V47mwpshkBI/AAAAAAAAaB8/RvpFLnPwwBcjTJgGMBDDYesZgqlKBDeCgCK4B/s1600/node-plugin-subl.png\"></a></p>\n<p>Cài đặt:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Nhấn <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+Shift+P</code> hoặc <code class=\"language-text\">Cmd+Shift+P</code> trên Linux/Windows/OS X</li>\n<li>Gõ  <code class=\"language-text\">install</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Package Control: Install Package</code></li>\n<li>Gõ <code class=\"language-text\">node</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Nodejs</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"javascript--nodejs-snippets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#javascript--nodejs-snippets\" aria-label=\"javascript  nodejs snippets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/JavaScript%20%26%20NodeJS%20Snippets\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Java​Script &#x26; Node​JS Snippets</a></h2>\n<p>Snippets giúp bạn tiết kiệm thời gian viết code rất nhiều. Nhất là các hàm dài và khó nhớ của Javascript.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://i.giphy.com/3o6ZsSVyRWQtoSJVkc.gif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/3o6ZsSVyRWQtoSJVkc.gif\"></a></p>\n<p>Cài đặt:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Nhấn <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+Shift+P</code> hoặc  <code class=\"language-text\">Cmd+Shift+P</code> trên Linux/Windows/OS X</li>\n<li>Gõ <code class=\"language-text\">install</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Package Control: Install Package</code></li>\n<li>Tìm và chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Java​Script &amp; Node​JS Snippets</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"jshint\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#jshint\" aria-label=\"jshint permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/JSHint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">JSHint</a></h2>\n<p>Công cụ kiểm tra lỗi cú pháp cho Javascript và Node.js</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-J7nE0oaEXqk/V471ZPhhaeI/AAAAAAAAaCI/h98jbEXf_pc0JHCNbJfuMYKGU1I7Sp6_wCLcB/s1600/jshint-duyetdev.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-J7nE0oaEXqk/V471ZPhhaeI/AAAAAAAAaCI/h98jbEXf_pc0JHCNbJfuMYKGU1I7Sp6_wCLcB/s1600/jshint-duyetdev.png\"></a></p>\n<p>Để cài JSHint trong sublime, trước tiên cần cài JSHint Package bằng NPM.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo npm install -g jshint</code></pre></div>\n<p>Sau đó cài đặt JSHint bằng Package Control như bình thường.</p>\n<h2 id=\"babel\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#babel\" aria-label=\"babel permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Babel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Babel</a></h2>\n<p>Babel đã quá nổi tiếng rồi, Package Babel hỗ trợ coding ES6, React với tệp mở rộng JSX.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hHnqzrhlgUY/V472sFiVLNI/AAAAAAAAaCY/cRVWJSBtvBg2xI_Qp3EP-ML9xgBP6i1AQCK4B/s1600/8e99bbdc99a285708a1495a6e3dd68916753906e.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hHnqzrhlgUY/V472sFiVLNI/AAAAAAAAaCY/cRVWJSBtvBg2xI_Qp3EP-ML9xgBP6i1AQCK4B/s640/8e99bbdc99a285708a1495a6e3dd68916753906e.png\"></a></p>\n<p>Cài đặt:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Nhấn <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+Shift+P</code> hoặc <code class=\"language-text\">Cmd+Shift+P</code> trên Linux/Windows/OS X</li>\n<li>Gõ <code class=\"language-text\">install</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Package Control: Install Package</code></li>\n<li>Tìm và chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Babel</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"babel-snippets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#babel-snippets\" aria-label=\"babel snippets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Babel%20Snippets\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Babel Snippets</a></h2>\n<p>Tương tự Java​Script &#x26; Node​JS Snippets, Babel Snippets cung cấp danh sách các snippets hữu ích cho React và ES6.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-n959RoTjV9s/V474ccvmq_I/AAAAAAAAaCs/3_KB3VeL8VwpgAkwFEK9hYb4Nj2mDahRwCK4B/s1600/babel-snippets-duyetdev.gif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-n959RoTjV9s/V474ccvmq_I/AAAAAAAAaCs/3_KB3VeL8VwpgAkwFEK9hYb4Nj2mDahRwCK4B/s1600/babel-snippets-duyetdev.gif\"></a></p>\n<p>Cài đặt:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Nhấn <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl+Shift+P</code> hoặc <code class=\"language-text\">Cmd+Shift+P</code> trên Linux/Windows/OS X</li>\n<li>Gõ <code class=\"language-text\">install</code>, chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Package Control: Install Package</code></li>\n<li>Tìm và chọn <code class=\"language-text\">Babel Snippets</code></li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/2016/07/sublime-text-plugin-nodejs.html","tagSlugs":["/tag/tutorial/","/tag/sublime-text/","/tag/js/","/tag/tutorials/","/tag/javascript/","/tag/react/","/tag/node-js/","/tag/node/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-07-20T11:14:00.000+07:00","description":"Hôm nay mình sẽ giới thiệu 1 số plugin cần có để lập trình Node.js trên Sublime.","tags":["Tutorial","sublime text","js","Tutorials","javascript","React","Node.js","Node"],"title":"Sublime Text Plugin nào cho lập trình viên Node.js","fbCommentUrl":"none"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2016/07/sublime-text-plugin-nodejs.html"}}}